# Image 1 - Hero Dish Shot
Style: Chinese Ink Wash (Sumi-e)
Aspect Ratio: 16:9
An elegant artistic illustration of Longjing shrimp (龙井虾仁): a white porcelain plate with glistening pink shrimp and fresh green Longjing tea leaves, steam rising gently, soft West Lake scenery in the background with willow trees and a traditional pavilion, delicate brushstrokes, muted greens and soft pinks with warm amber highlights, peaceful atmosphere capturing Hangzhou's refined tea cuisine culture, high quality digital art, museum-poster feel.

# Image 2 - Ingredients & Process
Style: Chinese Ink Wash (Sumi-e)
Aspect Ratio: 16:9
An educational illustration showing Longjing shrimp ingredients and preparation: fresh river shrimp on one side, premium Longjing green tea leaves in a traditional tea bowl on the other, with cooking elements (wok, ginger, scallions) arranged artistically between them, soft watercolor washes in greens and earth tones, minimalist composition emphasizing the connection between tea cultivation and culinary arts, high quality digital art.
